snippet.title: Where Is My Parking Spot - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Where is my parking spot!? You have that urge, that drive, You MUST get to that special parking spot! Somehow when you use the brakes it also leaks brake fluid? That's normal right?

Subscribe for more content!

Where Is My Parking Spot Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1374400/Where_Is_My_Parking_Spot/
Play the game jam version: https://sonicboomcolt.itch.io/where-is-my-parking-spot
